      "For the scenario proposed above:<br><br>Produce a rich picture showing the problem situation (you can use any format that you find helpful).<br>Produce a root definition, using CATWOE, of the system from the viewpoint of the university.<br>What transformations or activities are required to make sure that the root definition is supported?",
